content: Example Domain This domain is for use in illustrative examples in documents You may use this domain in literature without prior coordination asking for permission More information

Example Domains As described in RFC 2606 RFC 6761 a number of domains such as example com example org are maintained for documentation purposes These domains may be used as illustrative examples in documents without prior coordination with us They are not available for registration transfer We provide a web service on example domain hosts to provide basic information on purpose of domain These web services are provided as best effort but are not designed to support production applications While incidental traffic for incorrectly configured applications is expected please do not design applications that require example domains to have operating HTTP service Further Reading IANA functions coordinate Internet s globally unique identifiers are provided by Public Technical Identifiers an affiliate of ICANN
